      "content": "i know people say it gets better but i don't think i want it to. i'm just so done. everything is just so exhausting and the sadness is all there is left. i keep thinking about how much easier it would be if i just didn't have to wake up to this silence anymore. if i could just... stop everything. it feels like the only way to actually get some peace.",
